dct_title_s: Location Map of proposed Searsville Addition to Jasper Ridge Biological Preserve, Lands of Leland Stanford Junior University, 1976
dct_description_sm: Map of Stanford University campus and surrounding vicinity prepared by PWS, 15 Oct 1976. "Searsville Addition 320 +- Ac.," "Jasper Ridge Biological Preserve," and "Stanford Linear Accelerating Center" are all identified by legend. Underlying contour map prepared by CAB, Stanford University Planning Office, 15 Jan 1968, and revised 15 Jun 1970.
